# CakePHP application (`app/`)

- CakePHP 5.x, PHP 8.1+.
- Controllers: `src/Controller/`; Models (Table/Entity): `src/Model/`; Templates: `templates/`.
- Migrations: `cakephp/migrations` plugin, files in `config/Migrations/`.
- Code generation: `bin/cake bake <type> <name>` (e.g. `bake model Users`).
- Tests: PHPUnit in `tests/TestCase/`.
- Run: `composer test`, `composer cs-check` from `app/`, or `make test` / `make cs-check` from workspace root.

Check the app's own `composer.json` and `config/app.php` before assuming a
plugin (queue, DebugKit, API-only routing) is installed — CakePHP apps vary
more than a single-stack Laravel app does.
